# Fetched TCG set artwork — 20MB+ of PNGs from public APIs (Pokémon TCG / Scryfall).
# Regenerate locally with `node scripts/fetch-set-logos.mjs`. The artwork itself
# stays out of git; the generated registry (src/shared/setLogos.generated.ts)
# IS tracked so EAS Build / CI can resolve `@/shared/setLogos.generated`
# without re-running the fetch step.
assets/sets/
